    <item>
      <title>Newsom说，加利福尼亚准备与贸易伙伴交谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/newsom-says-california-ready-to-talk-with-trading-partners-m92wcdw0</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加利福尼亚州州长加文·纽瑟姆（Gavin Newsom）表示，他将建立新的国际贸易伙伴关系，以抵抗唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）提议的关税，将该州作为堡垒，以反对他所谓的“我们一生中最大的税收加息”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/newsom-says-california-ready-to-talk-with-trading-partners-m92wcdw0</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 14:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普关税担心袭击时，加拿大股票被纠正</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/canadian-stocks-tumble-into-correction-as-trump-tariff-fears-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大股票在周五进行了更正，因为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对主要贸易伙伴的关税引发了人们对经济衰退的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/canadian-stocks-tumble-into-correction-as-trump-tariff-fears-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 14:44:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着特朗普的关税激发溃败，纳斯达克100赛事进入熊市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-tariffs-drive-us-tech-shares-to-brink-of-bear-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳斯达克100号（NASDAQ 100）朝着一个熊市跌入熊市，因为它从2月的高点损失了20％，因为投资者曾经在布罗德市场（Broard Market）溃败中曾经飞行的科技股抛弃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-tariffs-drive-us-tech-shares-to-brink-of-bear-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 14:35:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
